def check(df):
    l = []
    columns = df.columns
    for col in columns:
        dtypes = df[col].dtypes
        nunique = df[col].nunique
        sum_null = df[col].isnull().sum()
        l.append([col, dtypes, nunique, sum_null])
    df_check = pd.DataFrame(l)
    df_check.columns=['column','dtypes','nunique','sum_null']
    return df_check 
check(df)
